snippet.title: Pico Driller · Game · Gameplay
snippet.description:
Play this game for free here: https://canarigames.itch.io/picodriller
Pico Driller is a retro-style digging game. Dig your way through as many layers of blocks as you can and be swift enough to avoid them falling on you. This game is made by Canari Games: http://www.canarigames.com/
